### ✅ Target State Definition
- **Platform**: Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript
- **Backend**: Firebase (Firestore, Auth, Functions)
- **Deployment**: Capacitor for desktop/mobile + Vercel for web
- **State Management**: Firestore real-time sync + IndexedDB fallback
- **RAM Target**: < 300MB (vs. current 500-700MB)

### ✅ Feature Parity
- Timer engine → TypeScript core module
- UI modes (normal/mini/nano) → React + Tailwind
- Config management → Firestore + localStorage
- Statistics → Firestore with real-time updates
- Sound system → Web Audio API
- Animations → CSS/WebGL sprites

